{"tid":778970,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PC] The Ruins Of The Lost Kingdom Chronicle (日本低需求任務式ARPG)","createTime":"2018-08-14T05:47:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T07:31:04.000Z","uid":49138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1e51c8d91e4981ea9188ea4711761ecb54dee1b3","tid":778970,"uid":49138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:47:11.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7noIL2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7noIL2f.jpg&h=c50fa547&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">遊戲類型：動作角色扮演類（ARPG）遊戲（可聯機）<br />\n遊戲製作：Tomoshibi<br />\n遊戲發行：Tomoshibi<br />\n遊戲平台：PC<br />\n發布時間：2013年10月4日<br />\n官方網站：<a href=\"http://www.tomoshibi.net/guide/rolo/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tomoshibi.net%2Fguide%2Frolo%2Findex.html&d=GoBdzZCraoQEJw9QjDPyFACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=e1b0170f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.tomoshibi.net/guide/rolo/index.html</a><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n遊戲介紹<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;The Ruins of the Lost Kindom&rdquo;系列作品（Ruinas，Rol，Rolo，Rolc），係由3個日本人組成嘅小團隊(Tomoshibi)所開發系列PC獨立遊戲。遊戲開發參考咗MHF和PSO，雖然遊戲引擎好舊，但係從遊戲嘅多元化同可玩性嚟講，完全不遜色任何一款大型動作類遊戲。ROLC嘅基本世界觀基於劍與魔法嘅世界，玩家需要扮演一位亡國的大將喺一個遠古王國嘅遺址中探索。遊戲分兩部分，一部分係&rdquo;<span style=\"color: orange;\">王國編</span>&rdquo;，擁有劇情和自由模式，玩家可以單人攜帶AI或者同朋友一起完成通關，探索古蹟，挑戰高難度BOSS等。<br />\n另一部分係&rdquo;<span style=\"color: green;\">大地篇</span>&rdquo;，類似MHF任務制設計，冇任何劇情故事，玩家需要不斷完成任務，挑戰高難度的BOSS ，收集稀有素材，打造裝備，練習高端COMBO等。<br />\n不過兩部分嘅玩家數據係完全分開，只有公會和揭示板係共通。（神裝係兩篇唔共通，要分開儲。）<br />\n簡單講，&rdquo;<span style=\"color: orange;\">王國篇</span>&rdquo;係單機故事向，不過就可以用返&rdquo;<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">大地篇</span>&rdquo;嘅AI或者同其他玩家連線。而&rdquo;<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">大地篇</span>&rdquo;就係多人遊戲向，最多可以6人打任務、8人對戰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n配置要求<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fQVR6w2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfQVR6w2.jpg&h=ff575689&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遊戲截圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LwgOrtY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLwgOrtY.jpg&h=3a2cb4b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KSvxhEw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKSvxhEw.jpg&h=5ff075cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遊戲下載<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.tomoshibi.net/guide/rolo/p04_0.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tomoshibi.net%2Fguide%2Frolo%2Fp04_0.html&d=GoBdzZCraoQEJw9QjDPyFACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=8b8b192c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.tomoshibi.net/guide/rolo/p04_0.html</a><br />\n1) 先dl &ldquo;基本パック&rdquo; 同 &rdquo;最新パッチ&rdquo;<br />\n2) 打開基本patch正常係會亂碼，唔使用解碼軟件住，可以照解壓到。<br />\n3) 第一個制係browse解壓路徑，第二個係確認。(建議解壓路徑當中係得英文數字)<br />\n4) 再打開最新patch同上面一樣，揀返基本patch嘅folder，解壓落去就得。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">遊戲前注意</span></div><br />\n- 解亂碼方法: windows7 可以用 pAppLocale；windows 10 建議用 Locale Emulator。<br />\n請先更新Direct x到最新版本。<br />\n- Windows 10 玩家要安裝埋Direct Play。<br />\n(<a href=\"https://support.ubi.com/en-gb/Faqs/000027439/Activate-DirectPlay-or-DirectDraw-Direct-3D-on-Windows-10\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.ubi.com%2Fen-gb%2FFaqs%2F000027439%2FActivate-DirectPlay-or-DirectDraw-Direct-3D-on-Windows-10&d=GoBdzZCraoQEJw9QjDPyFACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=028e1ae1\" target=\"_blank\">https://support.ubi.com/en-gb/Faqs/000027439/Activate-DirectPlay-or-DirectDraw-Direct-3D-on-Windows-10</a>)<br />\n- 建議關咗windows嘅firewall去。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFAQ<br />\n1) <ins>Router玩家自己開房冇人入到?</ins><br />\nGame入面係房主做Host畀其他玩家連接。所以房主要先開放Port: 2400 UPD或者直接用DMZ。唔想改 router可以考慮使用免費軟件Hamachi。<br />\n2) <ins>Game入面打唔到中文?</ins><br />\n因為隻game好舊，得Win7可以正常使用唔同中文輸入法打&rdquo;漢字&rdquo;；而Win10就暫時未揾到方法，唯有開個Notepad打&rdquo;漢字&rdquo;再Copy&amp;Paste落去。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n攻略網 Wiki<br />\n<a href=\"https://wikiwiki.jp/rolonline/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwikiwiki.jp%2Frolonline%2F&d=GoBdzZCraoQEJw9QjDPyFACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=8869bca2\" target=\"_blank\">https://wikiwiki.jp/rolonline/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">以上部份內容係由3DM同遊戲官網翻譯及轉載<br />\nLast edited 14-8-2018</span>"},{"pid":"a6a91d8ec5ce56e5975700637e0cbb0cc67117ff","tid":778970,"uid":49138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T08:38:09.000Z","msg":"基本遊戲內容係免費嘅，可以試玩吓先再決定買唔買佢嘅DLC。<br />\nDLC內容包括開放多啲人物角式、增加自創人物位置、提升免費人物能力，當然唔少得多啲職業、地圖、boss同埋裝備。<br />\n交易功能(遊戲內稱&quot;取引所&quot;)係要至少購買一個dlc patch先開放使用。<br />\nDLC暫時一共有12個，可以散買，但要買嘅話推薦直接買&quot;全拡張パッチセット&quot;。"},{"pid":"fd3d7011454c3292bae165476215c3e00b735f3b","tid":778970,"uid":49138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T13:16:38.000Z","msg":"完全冇人有興趣?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958250ca63791a7f6dba9dc38f17d9161b940f75","tid":778970,"uid":49138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T00:47:37.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8d2e7ba6923950960f9e0cdcba0702f2b6841aa","tid":778970,"uid":49138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T06:34:51.000Z","msg":"PV<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_LoGykNnx50\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_LoGykNnx50&d=GoBdzZCraoQEJw9QjDPyFACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=d511f530\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_LoGykNnx50</a>"},{"pid":"365564b336674b5fe3a748a1c95db1d3ad717948","tid":778970,"uid":49138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"958250ca63791a7f6dba9dc38f17d9161b940f75","tid":778970,"uid":49138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":