<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T02:56:30.000Z","msg":"雖然冇咩人氣, 但刷裝打王幾好玩㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34d213e4d6054e772d6bbf05b4bd8151e7f29ef5","tid":778970,"uid":49138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T14:26:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8612499bbda38698b666d4f4a827fb78eb68aecd","tid":778970,"uid":49138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}